---
export const prerender = false;
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lang = 'en';
---
<Layout title="Privacy & Security — Superpress" lang={lang}>
  <div class="desktop-only">
    <div class="bc"><div class="bc-in"><a href="/en">Home</a><span>›</span><span class="cur">Privacy & Security</span></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="mobile-only">
    <div class="m-bc"><a href="/en">Home</a><span>›</span><span style="color:var(--g800)">Privacy & Security</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="sec"><div class="sec-in" style="max-width:820px">
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--cond);text-transform:uppercase;font-size:28px;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:6px">Privacy & Security</h1>
    <div class="legal-updated">Last updated: July 2026</div>

    <p class="legal-p">
      Superpress Elektrik Malzemesi Sanayi ve Ticaret Ltd. Şti. ("Superpress") values the security and
      confidentiality of the personal data we obtain through our website, in accordance with Turkish Law No.
      6698 on the Protection of Personal Data ("KVKK"). This notice explains what data we collect and why, how
      we protect it, and how you can exercise your rights.
    </p>

    <h2 class="legal-h2">Data Controller</h2>
    <p class="legal-p">
      Under KVKK, your personal data is processed by Superpress Elektrik Malzemesi Sanayi ve Ticaret Ltd. Şti.
      as the data controller, within the scope described below.
    </p>

    <h2 class="legal-h2">What Personal Data We Collect</h2>
    <p class="legal-p">We only collect personal data that you choose to share with us through the contact form on our site. Our website does not have user accounts or a membership system.</p>
    <p class="legal-p legal-p-tight"><strong>Contact / Quote Request Form:</strong> Full name, email, phone number, product of interest, and your message.</p>
    <p class="legal-p legal-p-tight"><strong>Automatically Collected Technical Data:</strong> To prevent spam and automated (bot) submissions, we use Cloudflare Turnstile, which processes technical data such as your IP address. Our hosting infrastructure (Cloudflare) may also keep standard server logs for security purposes.</p>

    <h2 class="legal-h2">Purposes of Processing</h2>
    <ul class="legal-ul">
      <li>Responding to your contact and quote requests,</li>
      <li>Maintaining the security of our website and preventing misuse (spam, automated bot submissions, etc.),</li>
      <li>Fulfilling our legal obligations.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="legal-h2">Data Transfers</h2>
    <p class="legal-p">
      Your personal data is shared, to the extent necessary for the purposes above, with the technology
      providers we rely on: <strong>Resend</strong>, for delivering form notifications by email, and
      <strong>Cloudflare</strong>, for our hosting, database, and security (bot protection) infrastructure.
      These providers may operate servers outside Turkey; accordingly, your data may be processed under KVKK's
      provisions on cross-border data transfers. Other than as described here, your data is not shared with or
      sold to third parties except where legally required.
    </p>

    <h2 class="legal-h2">Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
    <p class="legal-p">
      Your personal data is processed on the basis of: being directly related to the establishment or
      performance of a contract, compliance with our legal obligations, our legitimate interest as data
      controller (provided this does not harm your fundamental rights and freedoms), and, where applicable,
      your explicit consent.
    </p>

    <h2 class="legal-h2">Retention Period</h2>
    <p class="legal-p">
      Your personal data is retained for as long as required by the purpose of processing, subject to any
      statutory limitation periods, and is then deleted, destroyed, or anonymized.
    </p>

    <h2 class="legal-h2">Cookies</h2>
    <p class="legal-p">
      As our site has no membership or comment system, we do not use cookies for those purposes. Cloudflare
      Turnstile, which we use to secure our forms, may store a temporary verification token in your browser to
      help distinguish genuine visitors from bots.
    </p>

    <h2 class="legal-h2">Your Rights Under KVKK</h2>
    <p class="legal-p">Under Article 11 of KVKK, you may apply to us to:</p>
    <ul class="legal-ul">
      <li>Learn whether your personal data is being processed,</li>
      <li>Request information if it has been processed,</li>
      <li>Learn the purpose of processing and whether it is used accordingly,</li>
      <li>Know the third parties to whom your data is transferred, domestically or abroad,</li>
      <li>Request correction of incomplete or inaccurate data,</li>
      <li>Request deletion or destruction of your data within the framework set out by KVKK,</li>
      <li>Request that any correction or deletion be notified to third parties to whom your data was transferred,</li>
      <li>Object to a result that is to your detriment arising solely from automated analysis of your data,</li>
      <li>Claim compensation for damages arising from unlawful processing of your data.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="legal-h2">How to Apply</h2>
    <p class="legal-p">
      To exercise the rights above, you may email us at <a href="mailto:info@superpress.com.tr">info@superpress.com.tr</a>
      or write to us at Bozkurt Mahallesi Dolapdere Caddesi No: 207 İç Kapı No: 1, Şişli / İstanbul, Türkiye.
    </p>
  </div></div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-updated { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--g400); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .legal-h2 { font-family: var(--cond);text-transform:uppercase; font-size: 20px; color: var(--navy); margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .legal-p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--g600); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .legal-p-tight { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .legal-p strong { color: var(--g800); }
  .legal-p a { color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; }
  .legal-ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 14px 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .legal-ul li { position: relative; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--g600); line-height: 1.7; }
  .legal-ul li::before { content: '•'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--blue); font-weight: 700; }
</style>
